reviewText: From the back of the box: "It's summer of the year 2000, and the waves at Malibu beach are rippin'. The surf is choice, the babes are fine, and the buds are tasty. You're just about to get high and take your babe for a ride, when an evil alien race crashes out of the sky, looking for a volleyball that can destroy the universe. This will be one summer to remember." Contains music by the Insect Surfers, dude!
